x^{a + ib}
x^{a + ib} = e^{a \ln(x) + i b \ln(x)}
 e^{a \ln(x) + i b \ln(x)} = e^{a \ln(x)} e^{i b \ln(x)} = x^a e^{i b \ln(x)} 
x^{a + ib} = x^a \cos(b \ln(x)) + i x^a \sin(b \ln(x)) 
x^{a + ib} = x^a e^{i b \ln(x)} 
